    "is substituted by the closest code vector of the codebook, resulting in the quantized embedding z q (x) ⊂ ℝ l×d c.",
    "Finally, z q (x) is decoded to generate the reconstructed output x ∈ {0, 1}",
    "149×21 having the original dimensions as the original sequence input x.",
